#### Running
./ArgSemSAT <param1> ... <paramN>
--help			 this help
-d 			 *HIGH* level of debug (very slow, very dense output)
-f <filename>		 input file name for a problem
-fo <format>		 format of the input file
-p <problem>		 problem to be solved
-a <additional>		 argument to check the acceptance
--formats		 list of supported file types
--problems		 list of supported problems
